## Firebase Function + Firestore

### Install

```
npm install -g firebase-tools
firebase login
npm run deploy
```

### Run function locally

Not work if connect to firestore. permission problem.

```
firebase emulators:start
```

### Method

```
[POST] https://us-central1-sogo-mock-server.cloudfunctions.net/webApi/contacts/

[GET] https://us-central1-sogo-mock-server.cloudfunctions.net/webApi/contacts/MEhK8T1Ri3kxXxz70lMt

[GET] https://us-central1-sogo-mock-server.cloudfunctions.net/webApi/contacts/

[DELETE] https://us-central1-sogo-mock-server.cloudfunctions.net/webApi/contacts/OgAzEgCB0Tp5YZGqOwoY
```